        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Image_1.png",
        "heading": "Your Buongiorno in Sydney CBD",
        "description": "<p><strong>At EATALO, coffee isn’t just part of the menu — it’s part of who we are. Our signature EATALO Blend is a smooth, full-bodied coffee, roasted to capture the heart of Italy in every sip, right here in Sydney CBD.</strong></p><p>Whether it’s your morning espresso, a creamy cappuccino or a quick long black on the go, we’re here to greet you with a smile and a loud “Buongiorno!”. From takeaway to dine-in, our coffee pairs perfectly with breakfast, lunch and everything in between.</p><p>From café mornings to office catering, every cup reflects our commitment to quality, consistency and genuine Italian hospitality. At EATALO, every coffee is made to brighten your day — one cup, one smile at a time.</p>"
