        "heading": "Our Head Chef & Italian Heritage",
        "description": "<p><strong>Raised in Umbria, Italy, John Thomas grew up in the kitchen, inspired by his Nonna’s love for cooking. From an early age, he learned that food is more than flavour — it’s tradition, family and a way to share joy.</strong></p><p>He later refined his craft working with one of Italy’s most renowned catering companies, Preludio, delivering high-end catering for events, weddings and large celebrations.</p><p>Now based in Sydney, Chef John brings this experience to EATALO, creating dishes that honour his roots while adding a modern touch — from café dining to office catering and corporate events.</p>"
